<step1>
<ptxt>PERFORM ACTIVE TEST</ptxt>
<atten4>
<ptxt>Performing the intelligent tester's ACTIVE TEST allows relay, VSV, actuator and other items to be operated without removing any parts. Performing the ACTIVE TEST early in troubleshooting is one way to save time. The DATA LIST can be displayed during the ACTIVE TEST.</ptxt>
</atten4>
